wlv.mt.tools
Class OpenFstWrapper

java.lang.Object
  wlv.mt.tools.OpenFstWrapper

public class OpenFstWrapper
extends java.lang.Object

This is a wrapper around OpenFst functionality. The operations it exposes are fstcompile, fstnbest, fsttopsort and fstprint

Author:
Catalina Hallett
